trans-unit.source: Represents an <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> property (and the value of the property) of a printing system hardware or software component.
trans-unit.target: 인쇄 시스템 하드웨어 또는 소프트웨어 구성 요소의 <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 속성 및 속성 값을 나타냅니다.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> class.
The name of the <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> class for the specified property.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 속성에 대해 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화합니다.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName` 철자를 사용 해야 몇몇 특정의 이름을 똑같이 <xref:System.Int32> 대/소문자를 포함 하는 인쇄 시스템 개체의 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> 의 속성을 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> "AveragePPM" 또는 "AveragePagesperMinute" 아닌지 "AveragePagesPerMinute" 개체를 입력 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The name of the <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
The value of <see cref="T:System.Object" /> the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> class for the specified attribute and gives it the specified value.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 특성에 대해 <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 클래스의 새 인스턴스를 초기화하고 여기에 지정된 값을 제공합니다.

trans-unit.source: The `attributeName` should be spelled exactly the same as the name of some particular <xref:System.Int32> property of a print system object, including casing.
trans-unit.target: `attributeName` 철자를 사용 해야 몇몇 특정의 이름을 똑같이 <xref:System.Int32> 대/소문자를 포함 하는 인쇄 시스템 개체의 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> property of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> object must be spelled "AveragePagesPerMinute", not "AveragePPM" or "AveragePagesperMinute".
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어는 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.AveragePagesPerMinute%2A> 의 속성을 <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> "AveragePPM" 또는 "AveragePagesperMinute" 아닌지 "AveragePagesPerMinute" 개체를 입력 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Provides implicit conversion from a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> (or from a pointer to such a property) to an <see cref="T:System.Int32" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> 또는 이러한 속성에 대한 포인터에서 <see cref="T:System.Int32" />로 암시적으로 변환합니다.

trans-unit.source: A pointer to the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> that is converted.
Provides implicit conversion to an <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> from a pointer to a <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" />.
The converted PrintInt32Property object to an Int32 object.
Gets or sets the value of the property that the <see cref="T:System.Printing.IndexedProperties.PrintInt32Property" /> represents.
The property cannot be set to the value that the calling code provides.
trans-unit.target: 호출 코드에서 제공하는 값으로 속성을 설정할 수 없는 경우
